  "prompt": "What is the average Outbrain's CTR for marketers?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Outbrain's average click-through rate (CTR) can vary widely based on multiple factors such as industry, the quality of the content, and targeting strategies. Generally, a typical CTR for content discovery platforms like Outbrain might range from 0.5% to 2%. However, it's essential to consider that these numbers can fluctuate and marketers often see different results based on their specific campaigns and audience engagement.\n\nFor the most accurate and current statistics, it would be best to consult Outbrain's official reports or industry case studies, as well as keep an eye on any industry benchmarks that may be published after 2023.",
